snippet.title: Ai Chan Plays Fushigi Yuugi Suzaku Ibun - Playstation 2 Gameplay - Yuu Watase design Konami
snippet.description:
Intro starts @00:00:19

Most dissappointing game of the new year. Fushigi Yuugi Suzaku Ibun has all the characters I want to see from the original anime, but the voice acting is sadly not the original cast, which makes a big NONO for da game... everything else ist just typical otome dating simulation.... What did they do here!! yuu watase sensei, why?? why????? 

#fushigiyuugigame  #suzakuibun #fushigiyuugips2
